{"tid":906593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【金馬風波】鞏俐臨場拒上台頒獎 李安尷尬：妳不上來跟我頒嗎 ？","createTime":"2018-11-18T06:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T16:16:56.000Z","uid":130626,"like":10,"dislike":271,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"34aeff74dfd567b15a9d0f2ac89caa597d933245","tid":906593,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:20:32.000Z","msg":"昨晚台灣金馬獎引爆中台大戰，憑《我們的青春，在台灣》奪最佳紀錄片的導演傅榆歷，在台上發表台獨言論，疑觸動了大陸人神經，上屆影帝凃們上台頒最佳女主角時，就以一句「中國台灣金馬獎」還擊，去到頒獎禮尾聲，大會原定安排李安和鞏俐齊齊頒發最佳劇情長片獎，但...鞏俐竟然拒絕上台！<br />\n當大會宣布頒發壓軸大獎最佳劇情長片，結果只有李安單拖出場，鞏俐坐在台下冇反應，不知是否台獨風波拒上台，還是想避開以《影》入圍的舊愛張藝謀！當台上播完入圍影片後，李安對台下嘅鞏俐講：「鞏俐，妳不上來跟我頒嗎？」鞏俐依然拒上台，令李安十分尷尬！<br />\n除了臨場拒上台頒獎外，鞏俐更創下評審團主席冇向傳媒解說評審過程嘅首例，結果又要勞煩李安出頭，代表鞏俐到媒體區跟媒體致意，改由有份參與評審會議嘅執行長聞天祥講解評審過程。李安只簡單表示鞏俐「不方便下來」，問到點解鞏俐冇按程序上台頒獎？李安尷尬表示：「她想跟他們評審同事坐在一起，就決定不上來了。」<br />\n據台灣傳媒報道，鞏俐拒上台可能跟台獨、中國台灣金馬獎等言論有關，另亦有工作人員估鞏俐臨時拒絕頒獎同台獨言論冇關，因噚日評審決選投票後，就傳出鞏俐黑面，似乎對金馬決賽評審投票結果唔滿意。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181118/large/1542510240_7515.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181118%2Flarge%2F1542510240_7515.jpg&h=ed2d1b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181118/large/1542510240_f340.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181118%2Flarge%2F1542510240_f340.jpg&h=5b7422c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181118/58927433\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181118%2F58927433&d=tg3Dda7iVq8UyaQIpyYsBGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=64a25277\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181118%2F58927433&h=31262c87\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181118/58927433</a>"},{"pid":"754d6a3ab16ea5affbff9b516649931a535ec782","tid":906593,"uid":10757,"like":353,"dislike":8,"score":345,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:24:34.000Z","msg":"條女都幾串"},{"pid":"5eece62cb21bd5104cb2ed4a0091a1d74a61ff44","tid":906593,"uid":105891,"like":421,"dislike":3,"score":418,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:25:01.000Z","msg":"點洗都好大陣大陸雞味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b2bf0d27e838a323e6adc1d73eb7688585e2ab","tid":906593,"uid":12994,"like":426,"dislike":3,"score":423,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:27:16.000Z","msg":"大陸妹始終都係大陸妹<br />\n上唔到大台"},{"pid":"e3527acdb516ddd4bbc1dbfacbbaec82e542ef84","tid":906593,"uid":38651,"like":111,"dislike":1,"score":110,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:27:53.000Z","msg":"鞏俐 啱晒你"},{"pid":"c84771016d3a22e277d923f4f7bfd450b7a3fc08","tid":906593,"uid":48104,"like":441,"dislike":1,"score":440,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:28:55.000Z","msg":"鞏俐咁愛國<br />\n佢放棄咗新加坡國籍未？"},{"pid":"76c725fd36abd525b1a7c9ef27f909424600a553","tid":906593,"uid":35790,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"d5b2bf0d27e838a323e6adc1d73eb7688585e2ab","tid":906593,"uid":12994,"like":426,"dislike":3,"score":423,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:27:16.000Z","msg":"大陸妹始終都係大陸妹<br />\n上唔到大台"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:30:22.000Z","msg":"人地係北方炎黃子孫<br />\n現在係新加坡人"},{"pid":"32cfbd72adeb0972c08c157a4635059665da7cc1","tid":906593,"uid":18955,"like":1,"dislike":114,"score":-113,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:30:39.000Z","msg":"綺夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646c0b4b7304c590ec112460159eb1b5dcfb2dfe","tid":906593,"uid":38143,"like":225,"dislike":1,"score":224,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:31:37.000Z","msg":"新加玻人鞏利咁愛中國做乜要移民"},{"pid":"955fa3a6a650c787b537c772cf7fdadbd9de83d8","tid":906593,"uid":38143,"like":175,"dislike":5,"score":170,"quote":{"pid":